{"type": "article", "id": 18142, "title": "户外沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-27T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122423JsuvNTwlSF0ea7fm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是法国设计师 Jean-Marie Massaud 为德国户外家具品牌 dedon 推出的沙发。沙发靠背上面连接了一个手工编织的遮阳蓬，有点像一个凉亭。光影透过遮阳蓬的缝隙漏下来，形成层层的纹路，遮阳透气之余，也令人感到放松。遮阳蓬的一侧开了一个圆形的口，让阳光直射，成为看书的地方。这张沙发也可以当做一张小床，目前还没有上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122419CZWq59HbcRTISrwY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.11002445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122420I8t9ci5mYnHpSwCL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122421c7ZKSbRNYxDhTOBf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72982885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122421tPHWr059QNShMB6k.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071224220uA3HfUv7jpOZCqa.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.32640587\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}